## Testing (Ubuntu Official Methods)

Test suite: `tests/qemu-test.sh` → `test-report.txt`

1. `dpkg --verify` — zero modified
2. `apt-get check` — zero broken
3. `dpkg --audit` — clean
4. os-release matches series
5. architecture = arm64
6. No excluded packages
7. Timers disabled
8. Initramfs overlay hook executable
9. /boot has: boot.img, dtbs/, overlays/, extlinux/
10. /overlay has: upper/, work/

